legacy.full_text: A major milestone in climate change👣: China🇨🇳 and the U.S. 🇺🇸have agreed to resume a working group on #climate cooperation and pledged a major ramp-up of #renewable energy during this decade. #APEC https://t.co/Ok7FxLbMrp

legacy.full_text: AI Safety Summit 2023 in #Britain🇬🇧: The agreement named "#Bletchley Declaration" was signed by over 25 nations, which marks a significant turning point in history. 🇨🇳#China will work with the 🇺🇸US, 🇪🇺EU and other countries to collectively manage the risk from #AI. https://t.co/B7dabwjjQx

Wu Zhaohui, China's vice minister of Science and Technology, stated that "countries regardless of their size and scale have #equal rights to develop and use AI," and that "China is willing to enhance our dialogue and communication in AI safety with all sides.” https://t.co/I8sXWUWBW0
